      Anchor Rage stands out as an extremely versatile single-wirebug move that fits into any lance
      playstyle. The counter state blocks incoming attacks and follows up with a powerful thrust
      while granting a raw attack buff based on the blocked attack's strength. This buff persists
      for 30 seconds or until weapon sheathing.
    </p>

