    </p>

    <SectionSubTitle title="Spiral Thrust" />
    <p>
      Spiral Thrust costs one wirebug and enables two directional dashes with significant offensive
      potential. The initial dash includes a Guard Point, and successful blocks trigger a 10-second
      blue glow indicating a 10% raw attack boost.
    </p>

    <GifCard src="https://giphy.com/embed/DPl5DdaeiBTbyCpWL1" title="Dash! Dash! Poke!" reversed>
